attr.title: Skautfold: Shrouded in Sanity
attr.desc: Discover the secrets of the estate, as you look for answers among the violent inhabitants. A strange and repelling madness took hold of the servants roaming the halls, and they will attack on sight, for their madness is one rooted in a deeper understanding of cosmic insignificance.
attr.inst: Purchase the game on Steam and copy all files into the assets folder. Only paid version is supported due to technical reasons.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game on [Steam](https://store.steampowered.com/app/444590/Skautfold_Shrouded_in_Sanity/) and copy all files into the `assets` folder. Only `paid` version is supported due to technical reasons.
